sequenceDiagram
  participant O as Serial orchestrator
  participant P as Parent adapter
  participant S as Sandpack iframe
  participant A as State Atlas builder

  O->>P: Execute one correlated fixture
  P->>S: Source + JSON props + session/run/fixture/nonce
  S-->>P: RENDER_COMMITTED
  Note over S: Wait 750 ms after meaningful commit
  S->>S: Inspect bounded layout and img candidates
  S-->>P: DETECTOR_EVIDENCE with bounded metadata
  P->>P: Validate source window, correlation and schema
  P->>P: Assign deterministic finding IDs
  P-->>O: Existing execution status + visual findings
  O->>O: Unmount fixture sandbox before next fixture
  O-->>A: Completed validated execution session
  A->>A: Preserve RunPlan order and derive categories
